              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z749281L-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Z749281L-line-1" n="1">If thou'rt a Deist, thy Plea I'l let pass;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z749281L-line-2" n="2">But if a Xian, thou talkst like an Ass.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z749281L-line-3" n="3">For if by Scripture thy Doctrine We trye</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z749281L-line-4" n="4">Thy pittyfull Iest will prove but a Lye.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z749281L-line-5" n="5">But Since (as a Beast) thou'st right to a Stall,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z749281L-line-6" n="6">Lett me recomend Thee to Saltor's Hall.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
